# fusion-cam.lap

[types]
AdditiveFEAAnalysisType: Thermal | Mechanical | ThermoMechanical
AdditiveFEACard: TitleCard | STLToleranceCard | LayersPerElementCard | AmbientTemperatureCard | FinalTemperatureCard | BuildPlateZBoundsCard | STLMapCard | ConvectionCard | PRMsCard | STLsCard | BuildPlateXYExtensionCard | AdaptivityCard | AnalysisTypeCard | BinaryOutputCard | EnsightOutputCard | NoOffCoreCard | OnCore1Card | CoarseningGenerationsCard | EndCard | MaterialCard | LaserPathGenerationCard | TransientCard | PropertyScalingCard | PowderTypeCard | FineLayerCountCard | AutomaticTimingCard | DiskCheckCard | GoldakCard | PowderCard | AutomaticMeshingCard | PowderBedYSymmetryCard | NewPRMGenerationMethodCard | InitialTemperatureCard | EvaporationTemperatureCard | RelaxationCard | OutputFileFrequencyCard | SolutionParametersCard | MechanicalRelaxationCard
AdditiveFEAGenerationType: MeshPreCheck | PRM | Result
AdditiveFEAMaterial: AISI4340AlloySteel | AlSi10Mg | CobaltChrome | Inconel625 | Inconel718 | Inconel718Plus | SAE304 | StainlessSteel174PH | StainlessSteel316 | Ti6Al4V
AdditiveFEAPowderType: Automatic | Scaled | Custom
AdditiveFEASTLConfiguration: Part | BuildPlate | Support | Ghost
AdditiveTechnologies: FFFTechnology | DEDTechnology | MPBFTechnology | MFJTechnology | BinderJettingTechnology | SLATechnology | SLSTechnology | NATechnology | OtherTechnology | EbeamTechnology
ArrangePriorities: VeryLowArrangePriority | LowArrangePriority | MediumArrangePriority | HighArrangePriority | VeryHighArrangePriority
ArrangePriorityTypes: VeryHighArrangePriorityType | HighArrangePriorityType | MediumArrangePriorityType | LowArrangePriorityType | VeryLowArrangePriorityType
ArrangeRotationTypes: GlobalArrangeRotationType | AllRotationsArrangeRotationType | NoneArrangeRotationType | Only180ArrangeRotationType | Only90And270ArrangeRotationType
ArrangeSolverTypes: Arrange2DTrueShapeSolverType | Arrange2DRectangularSolverType | Arrange3DSolverType
CAM3MFSupportInclusionType: NotIncluded | IncludeAsSupportType | IncludeAsModelType
CAMAdditiveContainerTypes: SupportCAMAdditiveContainerType | OptimizedOrientationCAMAdditiveContainerType | BodyPresetCAMAdditiveContainerType | AdditiveProcessSimulationCAMAdditiveContainerType
CAMEventChangeType: ErrorCAMEventChangeType | ToolCAMEventChangeType | ToolSwitchCAMEventChangeType | NameCAMEventChangeType | ParameterCAMEventChangeType
CAMEventState: CAMEventStateSuccessful | CAMEventStateDeferred | CAMEventStateErrorMissingOperation | CAMEventStateErrorMissingDocument | CAMEventStateErrorOther
GeneratedDataType: OptimizedOrientationGeneratedDataType | AdditiveFEAGeneratedDataType
InspectionPointState: WithinTolerance | AboveTolerance | BelowTolerance | Unprojected
MachineAnglePreferences: MachineAngleNoPreference | MachineAnglePreferNegative | MachineAnglePreferPositive
MachineAxisCoordinates: MachineCoordinate_None | MachineCoordinate_X_A | MachineCoordinate_Y_B | MachineCoordinate_Z_C
MachineAxisTypes: LinearMachineAxisType | RotaryMachineAxisType
MachineCoolant: MachineCoolant_FLOOD | MachineCoolant_MIST | MachineCoolant_THROUGH_TOOL | MachineCoolant_AIR | MachineCoolant_AIR_THROUGH_TOOL | MachineCoolant_SUCTION | MachineCoolant_FLOOD_MIST | MachineCoolant_FLOOD_THROUGH_TOOL
MachineElementInputType: MultiAxisElement | ToolingCapabilityElement | ExtruderElement | LaserElement
MachineInputTypes: MachineInputFromTemplate | MachineInputFromFile | MachineInputFromLibrary
MachineItemType: MachineItemType_TOOL | MachineItemType_TOOL_CUTTER | MachineItemType_TOOL_NONCUTTER | MachineItemType_STOCK | MachineItemType_FIXTURE | MachineItemType_MODEL | MachineItemType_MACHINE_PART | MachineItemType_TURRET_ACTIVE_TOOL | MachineItemType_TURRET_INACTIVE_TOOL | MachineItemType_INVALID
MachineNonTCPInterpolationMode: MachineNonTCPInterpolationMode_SynchronizedAxes | MachineNonTCPInterpolationMode_IndependentAxes
MachinePartTypes: BasicMachinePartType | AxisMachinePartType | ToolAttachmentMachinePartType | FixtureAttachmentMachinePartType
MachineResetOptions: MachineResetNever | MachineResetBeforeEveryOperation | MachineResetOnRewind | MachineResetBeforeOpAndOnRewind
MachineTCPInterpolationMode: MachineTCPInterpolationMode_SynchronizedAxes | MachineTCPInterpolationMode_IndependentAxes | MachineTCPInterpolationMode_ToolTip
MachineTemplate: GenericLathe | Generic3Axis | Generic4Axis | Generic5AxisHeadHead | Generic5AxisHeadTable | Generic5AxisTableTable | GenericFFF
MachiningMode: Avoid_MachiningMode | Machine_MachiningMode | Gouge_MachiningMode | Fixture_MachiningMode
MultiAxisDegreesPerMinuteType: MultiAxisDegreesPerMinuteType_Standard | MultiAxisDegreesPerMinuteType_Combination
MultiAxisFeedMode: MultiAxisFeedMode_InverseTime | MultiAxisFeedMode_DegreesPerMinute | MultiAxisFeedMode_ProgrammerdFeedrate
MultiAxisInverseTimeUnit: MultiAxisInverseTimeUnit_Seconds | MultiAxisInverseTimeUnit_Minutes
MultiAxisRetractPreference: MultiAxisRetractPreference_RetractAtApex | MultiAxisRetractPreference_StayAtApex
MultiAxisRewindPreference: MultiAxisRewindPreference_RewindAtLinear | MultiAxisRewindPreference_RewindAtRapid
MultiAxisRotationTypes: MultiAxisRotationType_SingleAxis | MultiAxisRotationType_AllAxes | MultiAxisRotationType_XYAxes | MultiAxisRotationType_XZAxes | MultiAxisRotationType_YZAxes
MultiAxisSingularityLinearizeMethod: MultiAxisSingularityLinearize_Linear | MultiAxisSingularityLinearize_Rotary
OperationBaseEventTypes: ErrorOperationBaseEventType | CommandStartedOperationBaseEventType | GenerationStartedOperationBaseEventType | ChangeOperationBaseEventType | GenerationStartingOperationBaseEventType | CommandButtonPressedOperationBaseEventType
OperationStates: IsValidOperationState | IsInvalidOperationState | SuppressedOperationState | NoToolpathOperationState
OperationStrategyTypes: AdaptiveClearing2D | Pocket2D | Face | Contour2D | Slot | Trace | Thread | Bore | Circular | Engrave | AdaptiveClearing | PocketClearing | Parallel | Contour | Ramp | Horizontal | Pencil | Scallop | Spiral | Radial | MorphedSpiral | Projection | Drilling | Jet2D | TurningChamfer | TurningFace | TurningGroove | TurningPart | TurningProfile | TurningProfileGroove | TurningStockTransfer | TurningThread | SteepAndShallow | Flow | Flow2 | RotaryFinishing | Chamfer2D | Morph | MultiAxisContour | MultiAxisMorph | RestFinishing | Swarf | SurfaceInspection | ManualInspection | ProbeWCS | ProbeGeometry | PartAlignment | PathMeasure | ManualMeasure
OperationTypes: MillingOperation | TurningOperation | JetOperation | AdditiveOperation
PostCapabilities: Undefined | Milling | Turning | SetupSheet | Intermediate | Jet | Cascading | Additive | Inspection | MachineSimulation
PostOutputUnitOptions: DocumentUnitsOutput | InchesOutput | MillimetersOutput
PostProcessExecutionBehaviors: PostProcessExecutionBehavior_OmitInvalidAndEmptyOperations | PostProcessExecutionBehavior_Fail | PostProcessExecutionBehavior_PostAll
PrintSettingItemTypes: GENERAL | EXPORTER
RecognizedPocketBottomType: RecognizedPocketBottomTypeFlat | RecognizedPocketBottomTypeThrough | RecognizedPocketBottomTypeChamfer | RecognizedPocketBottomTypeFillet | RecognizedPocketBottomTypeOther
SetupChangeEventType: Arbitrary | PrintSettingSelection
SetupSheetFormats: HTMLFormat | ExcelFormat
SetupStockModes: FixedBoxStock | RelativeBoxStock | FixedCylinderStock | RelativeCylinderStock | FixedTubeStock | RelativeTubeStock | SolidStock | PreviousSetupStock
StrategyRegistrationIssues: SkipAll_StrategyRegistrationIssues | CancelOnParameterCollisions_StrategyRegistrationIssues | CancelOnMetaparameterCollisions_StrategyRegistrationIssues | CancelOnUnsupporedMetaparameters_StrategyRegistrationIssues | CancelOnAll_StrategyRegistrationIssues

